  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier, you can predict an ally’s success, bolstering others’ resolve. As a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Swift-Actions\">swift action</a>, you can shout an inspiring prediction, granting each ally within 50 feet who can hear you a +4&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Luck-Bonus\">luck bonus</a>&nbsp;on her next&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Attack-Roll\">attack roll</a>, saving throw, or skill check.</p>"
